About Us 

Tough coatings for harsh environments. 
Hayden Corporation is an ISO 9002-2008 registered provider of thermal spray coatings and other wear and corrosion control surfaces, providing comprehensive pre-surfacing and post-surfacing services including preparatory machining, finish grinding and metallurgical coating quality analysis.
We focus on flexibility and strive to meet a broad range of coating requirements with high-quality surfaces and the fastest possible delivery.
Our firm was founded in 1919 on the principle of providing superior service to our customers. Since then, our customer base has grown far more diverse. Our customers’ industries and needs are increasingly varied and challenging; and our goal of excellent service has remained the same.
We understand that coating technology is often not a core competency for our customers, so we make every effort to provide the information customers need to make sound, informed decisions.
Click here to learn more about Hayden Corp. history.

 








