–  About Hayden
Hayden Corporation is an ISO 9002-2008 registered provider of thermal spray coatings and other wear and corrosion control surfaces, providing comprehensive pre-surfacing and post-surfacing services including preparatory machining, finish grinding and metallurgical coating quality analysis.
 
We focus on flexibility and strive to meet a broad range of coating requirements with high-quality surfaces and the fastest possible delivery.
 

+ Our Beliefs
+ Quality Certifications
+ History






Tough Coatings for Harsh Environments

Rugged, harsh service environments demand optimal performance from all machinery and parts. At Hayden Corporation, we believe that your parts should survive the most extreme service environments.
 
The extreme conditions your parts face demand specialized talent and processes. Our solutions-based expert team of craftsmen and technicians know the best solutions to the greatest abrasion, adhesion, corrosion, heat, and other wear problems affecting your parts.












